The EIB, the European Union's bank, is seeking to recruit for its Corporate Services Directorate, Buildings and Logistics Department, Workplace Management & Mobility Division at its headquarters in Luxembourg, a Head of Business Travel Unit*. This is a full time position at grade 5/6.
